platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: スピード&ドリフト：エクストリームレーシング

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Conquer street and sky in Gameloft’s fastest racing game yet, a mix of high-octane driving and incredible jumps that harkens back to the age of San Francisco Rush and classic Burnout. Pairing white-knuckle action with an array of career and online modes, it sets a new standard for arcade racers on the App Store.
